  "title": "Therapy Assistant (Nursing Home - West Coast)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibility</strong></p>\n<p>Provide physical, emotional and social care for our nursing home residents.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<p>· Assist therapists to deliver therapy exercise according to care plan</p>\n<p>· Supervise the elderly in practising activities of daily living</p>\n<p>· Facilitate small group activities and conduct bedside therapy exercise</p>\n<p>· Maintain, clean and sterilize rehabilitation equipment</p>\n<p>· Ensure safety of the elderly during rehabilitation sessions</p>\n<p>- Assist with feeding residents</p>\n<p>· Administrative duties</p>\n<p>· Other duties assigned by supervisor</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>· Certificate in Therapy Support</p>\n<p>· Passionate in caring for the elderly.</p>\n<p>· Good communication and interpersonal skills</p>\n<p>- able to commit work schedule Monday to Friday and alternate Saturday (half day)</p>",
