    "description": "<p>THE LENTOR RESIDENCE</p>\n<p>The Lentor Health Group is rapidly expanding and will be operating 1,300 beds in 5 nursing homes &amp; 3 senior care centres located across Singapore. Great career advancement opportunities for achievers!</p>\n<p>We are accredited by Singapore Nursing Board as a Clinical Education Centre. Our care team consists of SNB recognised Clinical Instructors and ITE trained OJT trainers. Training is integral in providing quality care for our residents and clients. We provide a comprehensive continuous training program for our care staff as they continue to grow with us.</p>\n<p>Established in 1997, The Lentor Residence located on Lentor Avenue is a 208 beds nursing home with senior day care services. We provide holistic care and quality services for our beloved seniors to live a healthy lifestyle.</p>\n<p>Join us with a mission, create a home of choice with professional care from the heart.</p>",
